{"tid":1742180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"($2教學文) Popo破壞巴士，一於由政府買單","createTime":"2019-11-20T16:09:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T17:42:03.000Z","uid":68779,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fa09aba59a97637600d56f1d8ec7ede8caff2b96","tid":1742180,"uid":68779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T16:09:50.000Z","msg":"之前popo已經多次破壞巴士，巴士公司幫左我地咁多冇理由要佢地自己買單\b，<span style=\"color: red;\">教大家用$2大大力懲罰巴士公司，而且由政府代popo買單</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/74469301_10157843567066468_1927910596112547840_n.jpg?_nc_cat=108&amp;_nc_oc=AQkMyAFpSkBjImS02ke89Z9ca5bJQqxcNAb1irTdwmlF_WvFiYMiOFR9CXdT0jC_rus&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-1.fna&amp;oh=52c723748e10d23db100238d24ad6b10&amp;oe=5E59AE0B\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BnUXdJp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBnUXdJp.png&h=25a4f40a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-hNafau0RIYo/Uq0-ZUcumdI/AAAAAAAAFKc/z38Jq1SvSVE/s1600/$2+%E9%95%B7%E8%80%85%E5%85%AB%E9%81%94%E9%80%9A%E5%8D%A1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-hNafau0RIYo%2FUq0-ZUcumdI%2FAAAAAAAAFKc%2Fz38Jq1SvSVE%2Fs1600%2F%242%2B%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%2585%25AB%25E9%2581%2594%25E9%2580%259A%25E5%258D%25A1.jpg&h=7a647373&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當一程大西北巴士$22, 綠卡比左$2, 餘低果$20會由政府買單。<br />\n一日來回最基本政府會回番$40比巴士公司，只係計一個月20日都已經就$800.<br />\n就算只係有10萬人咁樣懲罰巴士，<span style=\"color: red;\">一個月已經幫巴士公司回血$80,000,000.</span> 係八千萬呀！<br />\n八千萬可以換到好多架巴士救人，<span style=\"color: red;\">巴士真係救到好多人</span>，之前旺角都係靠咁樣做先救到唔少人。<br />\n大家要報廢巴士時可能都有顧慮，但依家由政府買單，大家可以果斷行動。<br />\n前幾日油麻地如果出到巴士陣一定可以反敗為勝<br />\n依次上左一堂，下次唔會再犯依個錯誤，<span style=\"color: red;\">一定會用盡巴士陣，唔會再失去任何一位</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WzJfYpt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWzJfYpt.jpg&h=685e3df0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BADPjMW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBADPjMW.png&h=15cf1c29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋唔好再坐黨鐵，就算有綠卡都唔好坐，因為同道理，餘低既車費都係由政府比番黨鐵，<span style=\"color: red;\">變相黨鐵完全唔會蝕錢</span>，唯一可以做就係唔坐黨鐵一蚊都賺唔到。"},{"pid":"a5d17fc2e6984b0b236862444382662e6376a5c5","tid":1742180,"uid":68779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T16:13:47.000Z","msg":"支持既就留個言啦，聽日要聽到高音既do do八達通聲，do一次就可以幫巴士公司回血$20, 仲要由政府買單，唔係唔do呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e85588c6df9e4c3577f98c827370f51bc470ad39","tid":1742180,"uid":21924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T16:16:05.000Z","msg":"俾完車費再拍綠咭無犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ba37c8f34f834bab1aaca4f1986d443af7dcf1c","tid":1742180,"uid":171314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T16:16:12.000Z","msg":"靜靜地贏都唔得...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2268ba267c249e0098893ffe97e870717c94f42b","tid":1742180,"uid":114360,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T16:16:54.000Z","msg":"俾完車費再拍綠咭無犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77a5e15b2e42a1e9839ab54e6d740a8b56abc8d0","tid":1742180,"uid":171314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ba37c8f34f834bab1aaca4f1986d443af7dcf1c","tid":1742180,"uid":171314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T16:16:12.000Z","msg":"靜靜地贏都唔得...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\"